title: Travel Leaders Group Announces Leadership Changes
text:
Last updated: 02:47 PM ET, Wed September 09 2015 Travel Leaders Group Announces Leadership Changes Travel Agent | Travel Leaders Group | Patrick Clarke | September 09, 2015 
PHOTO: Barry Liben will soon take over as president and CEO of Tzell Travel Group. (Courtesy of Travel Leaders Group) 
After seven years at the helm, Travel Leaders Group announced Wednesday that CEO Barry Liben is leaving his position to take over as president and CEO of Tzell Travel Group, a division of Travel Leaders Group.
